OL,3,CSpeculation over Ryan Giggs return to
OL,4,CWales manager role
OL,6,FRichard Morgan takes a look at who
OL,7,Fcould take the top spot in Wales
OL,8,Ffootball...
OL,10,FFormer Wales boss Ryan Giggs has been
OL,11,Fnamed as one of the possible
OL,12,Fcontenders to succeed Rob Page.
OL,14,FThe ex-Manchester United winger
OL,15,Fpreviously held the job in the run up
OL,16,Fto the 2022 World Cup before he left
OL,17,Fwhile facing trial for domestic
OL,18,Fviolence allegations. Those charges
OL,19,Fwere dropped and he was found not
OL,20,Fguilty in July 2023.
