OL,3,CSpeculation over Ryan Giggs return to
OL,4,CWales manager role
OL,6,FHe has since returned to football,
OL,7,Ftaking on the role of director at
OL,8,FSalford City FC earlier this year.
OL,10,FReports in The Times now reveal Giggs
OL,11,Fcould be set to take the top spot back
OL,12,Fafter the man who stepped into his
OL,13,Fshoes in 2022 - then assistant coach
OL,14,Fand former teammate Rob Page - has
OL,15,Fbeen sacked.
OL,17,FRob Page's departure followed a string
OL,18,Fof disappointing results and the
OL,19,Fside's failure to qualify for Euro
OL,20,F2024.
