OL,3,CSpeculation over Ryan Giggs return to
OL,4,CWales manager role
OL,6,FBut it's not just Giggs' name that has
OL,7,Fbeen thrown into the mix, here's a
OL,8,Flook at some of the others in line for
OL,9,Fthe top job...
OL,11,FThe former Wales captain, with 78 caps
OL,12,Fto his name, is currently caretaker in
OL,13,Fcharge of Burnley following Vincent
OL,14,FKompany's departure to Bayern Munich.
OL,16,F44-year-old Bellamy played for
OL,17,FLiverpool, Manchester City, Newcastle
OL,18,Fand West Ham and first began his
OL,19,Fcoaching career at hometown club
OL,20,FCardiff when he took charge of the
OL,21,FBluebirds academy.
