OL,6,FBellamy came within a whisker of
OL,7,Fsucceeding Chris Coleman as Wales
OL,8,Fmanager in 2018. It was down to him
OL,9,Fand Giggs and the six-man FAW
OL,10,Fcommittee making the decision were
OL,11,Fsplit 3-3 on the two men.
OL,13,FIn the end it came down to the casting
OL,14,Fvote of then FAW President David
OL,15,FGriffiths and he plumped for Giggs.
