OL,6,FThe former technical director and
OL,7,Fassistant manager is currently at Como
OL,8,F1907 where he has overseen the
OL,9,FLombardy club's return to Serie A.
OL,10,FRoberts, 58, was at Chris Coleman's
OL,11,Fside when Wales reached the semi-
OL,12,Ffinals of Euro 2016.
OL,14,FAnglesey-born Roberts has also been
OL,15,Ftechnical director of the Moroccan
OL,16,FFootball Federation and coached
OL,17,Fdifferent age-grade teams in Wales.
OL,19,FHe is currently the bookies' best bet
OL,20,Fto succeed Page.
