OL,6,FThe former Arsenal and France striker
OL,7,Fmight seem an unlikely choice but
OL,8,Fafter gaining his coaching badges in
OL,9,FWales, it's said he has a real
OL,10,Faffinity with the country.
OL,12,FHenry, 46, first moved into coaching
OL,13,Fin 2015 taking on the Arsenal Youth
OL,14,Fsquad.
OL,16,FSince then he has spent time with
OL,17,FMonaco and Belgium and the Frenchman
OL,18,Fcurrently manages his country's U21
OL,19,Fside.
