OL,6,FHe was swiftly appointed the new
OL,7,Fmanager of Sunderland but left after
OL,8,Ffailing to keep them in the
OL,9,FChampionship.
OL,11,FCould Coleman make a comeback?
OL,13,FAnother former Wales manager, Hughes
OL,14,Fhas extensive experience at Blackburn,
OL,15,FManchester City, Fulham, QPR, Stoke,
OL,16,FSouthampton and most recently Bradford.
OL,18,FHe was sacked from that role after
OL,19,Fjust 19 months in charge following the
OL,20,Fteam's failure to win promotion.
