OL,6,F60-year-old Hughes made his
OL,7,Finternational debut for Wales in 1984,
OL,8,Fwhen he scored against England just 17
OL,9,Fminutes into the match.
OL,11,FA rising star, he went onto play for
OL,12,FManchester United and Chelsea before
OL,13,Fbecoming the manager of Wales in 1999,
OL,14,Foverseeing the side that came so close
OL,15,Fto qualifying for the 2004 European
OL,16,FChampionships - before being knocked
OL,17,Fout by Russia.
